	   <tr><td colspan=2>As long as you can keep your agi above 75 with this earring on, it rocks.<br><br>18 raw ac will convert to approx 35 ac, depending on class. each 5 agi you lose, will subtract 1 point of non-raw ac. <br><br>35 - 7 = 28<br> you still gain 28 ac from this item<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
