	   <tr><td colspan=2>Many people think otherwise. High agi can prevent the chance of being hit at all in the first place (where as AC lowers the ammount of damage taken- makes sence). This means to casters that when they're under attack, they won't get interupted as often with high agi. Then again, AC is valuable to any class, so it's really just something you have to test and find out on your own.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
